NZBGet is a binary newsgrabber, which downloads files from usenet based
on information given in nzb-files. Descriptino of nzb format is available
at http://docs.newzbin.com/

It offers the following features:

* Console interface, using either a plain text, a coloured text or a
  fully interactive ncurses interface
* Basic client/server model, allowing easy additions to the download queue.
* Bandwidth throtteling
* Multiple servers
* Multiple connections
